ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:

This project is based on the DR2G27 project by Aely0:
- Original repository: https://github.com/Aely0/DR2G27
- Original license: MIT
- Original author: Aely0

The core G27 LED control functionality and DiRT Rally 2.0 telemetry integration
were originally developed by Aely0. This fork extends that work with:
- Multi-game support (Forza Horizon 5)
- Enhanced CLI interface
- Improved error handling and architecture
- Trait-based telemetry parsing system